properties.name: keyEventTarget
properties.description:
The EventTarget that will be firing relevant KeyboardEvents. Set it to
`null` to disable the listeners.

properties.name: stopKeyboardEventPropagation
properties.description:
If true, this property will cause the implementing element to
automatically stop propagation on any handled KeyboardEvents.

properties.name: _imperativeKeyBindings
properties.description: own properties of everything on the "prototype".

properties.name: animating
properties.description: Indicates if the carousel is beeing animated (Transition)

properties.name: loop
properties.description:
Determines if the carousel should be looped.
This affects the controls and the drag and drop functionality.
Set to `true` if you need to loop the slides.

properties.name: end
properties.description: Returns true when the carousel has reached the last slide.

properties.name: showNext
properties.description: Determines if the next button should be displayed.

properties.name: showPrev
properties.description: Determines if the previous button should be displayed.

properties.name: _dots
properties.description:
Returns an array with the slides.
This will be used to create the dot controls.

properties.name: acceptedChildNodeNames
properties.description: Accepted node names as children, passed in via <slot>

methods.name: addOwnKeyBinding
methods.description:
Can be used to imperatively add a key binding to the implementing
element. This is the imperative equivalent of declaring a keybinding
in the `keyBindings` prototype property.

methods.name: removeOwnKeyBindings
methods.description: When called, will remove all imperatively-added key bindings.

methods.name: keyboardEventMatchesKeys
methods.description: Returns true if a keyboard event matches `eventString`.

methods.name: ready
methods.description: Ready event

methods.name: _slotChanged
methods.description: On slot change

methods.name: _prevKey
methods.description: Go to the previous slide with keybindings

methods.name: _nextKey
methods.description: Go to the next slide with keybindings

methods.name: _autoAnimate
methods.description: Observer on auto to turn on and off the feature

methods.name: next
methods.description: Go to next slide

methods.name: prev
methods.description: Go to previous slide

methods.name: _iconDot
methods.description: Switch the icon if the item is selected

methods.name: _selectedObserver
methods.description: Listen for changes on the selected item

methods.name: _lazyContent
methods.description:
Lazy load content for the given slider number
Replaces 'data-src' attribute to 'src'.

methods.name: _computeShowNext
methods.description: Determine if it should show the next button

methods.name: _computeShowPrev
methods.description: Determine if it should show the next button

methods.name: _computeDots
methods.description: Returns the dots array

methods.name: _computeEnd
methods.description: Determines if the current item is the last one on the list

methods.name: _normalize
methods.description: Returns a valid value

methods.name: _calcPercentage
methods.description: Returns the percentage that will to position the icon

methods.name: _drag
methods.description: Listen for track and move the container

methods.name: _computeIconPrev
methods.description: Compute icon previews

methods.name: _computeIconNext
methods.description: Compute icon next

methods.name: _translateObserver
methods.description: Translate swipe observer

methods.name: _returnDragPosition
methods.description: Compute translate swipe

methods.name: _computeContainerHeight
methods.description: Compute items container height

methods.name: _computeControls
methods.description:
Compute Controls
Returns true if needs to display the control.s

methods.name: _event
methods.description: Fire event
